 "remarks": "Wonderful opportunity to live in a spacious, light-filled 1-bedroom Norwalk ranch style condo that lives like a private home! Tucked away in a quiet, well-maintained complex with low common charges, this inviting residence features its own private front-door entrance and beautiful hardwood flooring throughout. Enjoy generously sized, airy rooms and an eat-in kitchen with sliders that open to your private deck-perfect for morning coffee or outdoor entertaining. Modern comforts include a highly coveted in-unit washer and dryer, abundant closet space, and an additional basement/crawl space for extra storage. This turn-key gem offers the ultimate convenience, located just minutes from Metro-North trains, Norwalk Hospital, premium shopping, vibrant dining, and everything Norwalk has to offer. Combining comfort, convenience, and incredible value, this is the perfect place to call home!",
